The final category winners will be announced at the World Media Awards reception at the Ham Yard Hotel in London on Thursday, 6 April along with the grand prix winner, which will be selected by the jury from amongst the category winners. View the 2017 shortlist here. As well as receiving a prestigious trophy on the night, all victors will see their work celebrated in an advertising campaign valued at &#x20ac;500 000, which will run across the World Media Group's leading international media brands: The Washington Post, The Wall Street Journal, Time, The New York Times, National Geographic, Newsweek, Fortune, Forbes, The Economist and Bloomberg.